		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <p id="ViKbZv" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
            GSA has a FAR deviation
that allows use of the clauses in paragraphs (a) and (b) of this
section in lieu of the FAR clause at <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_227_17"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.227-17</xref>.
         </p>
			      <ol id="d501e19" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li id="QyXUrm" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d496e23" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
						            <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  Except as
provided in paragraph (b) of this section, insert <xref href="552.227-70.dita#GSAM_552_227_70"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">552.227-70</xref>,
Government Rights (Unlimited),in lieu of the FAR clause
at
                  <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_227_17"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.227-17</xref>, in solicitations
and contracts for—
               </p>
					          <ol class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li id="i1am4jw" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="8pqgglb" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
